{"tid":1537854,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一comment 俾翻中環海濱我地!!!","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:33:38.000Z","uid":66720,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"da4ddcfe12e39a809b93e5b2b8c14410e6366138","tid":1537854,"uid":66720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">團體擬將<span style=\"color: red;\">中區軍用碼頭改劃休憩用地</span> 軍事船隻停泊時暫停開放</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n立法會早前審議修訂《2019年軍事設施禁區令》的附屬法例，將其中一幅中環海濱長廊移交解放軍作軍事碼頭，一度引起社會迴響，被指等同「海濱送中」。而該附屬法例已於今年6月29日生效。<br />\n<br />\n就城規會資料所示，中環海濱關注組日前向城市規劃委員會提交申請，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">要求除了部分現有的構築物及登岸梯級外，其餘地方擬改劃為「休憩用地」，以將整個中區海濱向公眾開放。不過，當有軍事船隻進入香港並停泊時，便需暫時停止向公眾開放。</span></span>城規會將於11月1日開會討論有關申請。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海港是港人特別公有資產</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中環海濱關注組又在文件中提及改劃的理由，<span style=\"color: gold;\">指用於香港防務工作的軍事設施，已設置在香港其他地方，故無需在此敏感地帶永久設立軍事設施</span>。<br />\n<br />\n此外，申請人又指，為配合海濱事務委員會及其專責小組的建議，並按照<span style=\"color: gold;\">《保護海港條例》</span>的原則，海港應作為香港人的特別公有資產。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">20/9/2019就截止公眾提出意見 <br />\n現時係0個comment<br />\n跪求大家一人一comment <br />\n向城規會表示香港人支持呢個規劃申請!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/en/plan_application/Y_H24_9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Fen%2Fplan_application%2FY_H24_9.html&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3EngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=0f5b2e5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/en/plan_application/Y_H24_9.html</a>(英文版)<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Y_H24_9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Ftc%2Fplan_application%2FY_H24_9.html&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3EngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=87412d47\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Y_H24_9.html</a>(中文版)<br />\n<br />\n利申: 本絲為P牌會員 有咩做得唔啱歡迎提點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n了解更多請睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/369693/%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%80%E8%BB%8D%E7%94%A8%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%83%E4%BC%91%E6%86%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0-%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E8%88%B9%E9%9A%BB%E5%81%9C%E6%B3%8A%E6%99%82%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F369693%2F%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%258A%2583%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%2586%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2588%25B9%25E9%259A%25BB%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25B3%258A%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3EngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=7da926c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/369693/%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%80%E8%BB%8D%E7%94%A8%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%83%E4%BC%91%E6%86%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0-%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E8%88%B9%E9%9A%BB%E5%81%9C%E6%B3%8A%E6%99%82%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Attachment/20190830/s12a_Y_H24_9_0_gist.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Ftc%2Fplan_application%2FAttachment%2F20190830%2Fs12a_Y_H24_9_0_gist.pdf&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3EngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=0ca52639\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Attachment/20190830/s12a_Y_H24_9_0_gist.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"31643031545c645fbbf93932a8033f614ca344df","tid":1537854,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"341a2e7f5cf93e15f625f2b144daf065fa801404","tid":1537854,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8B39Niu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8B39Niu.png&h=c9eeccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr